57    protected function writeDrawingRelations(AbstractSlideAlias $pSlideMaster, XMLWriter $objWriter, int $relId)
58    {
59        if ($pSlideMaster->getShapeCollection()->count() > 0) {
60            // Loop trough images and write relationships
61            $iterator = $pSlideMaster->getShapeCollection()->getIterator();
62            while ($iterator->valid()) {
63                if ($iterator->current() instanceof ShapeDrawingFile || $iterator->current() instanceof ShapeDrawingGd) {
64                    // Write relationship for image drawing
65                    $this->writeRelationship(
66                        $objWriter,
67                        $relId,
68                        'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/image',
69                        '../media/' . str_replace(' ', '_', $iterator->current()->getIndexedFilename())
70                    );
71                    $iterator->current()->relationId = 'rId' . $relId;
72                    ++$relId;
73                } elseif ($iterator->current() instanceof ShapeChart) {
74                    // Write relationship for chart drawing
75                    $this->writeRelationship(
76                        $objWriter,
77                        $relId,
78                        'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/chart',
79                        '../charts/' . $iterator->current()->getIndexedFilename()
80                    );
81                    $iterator->current()->relationId = 'rId' . $relId;
82                    ++$relId;
83                } elseif ($iterator->current() instanceof Group) {
84                    $iterator2 = $iterator->current()->getShapeCollection()->getIterator();
85                    while ($iterator2->valid()) {
86                        if ($iterator2->current() instanceof ShapeDrawingFile ||
87                            $iterator2->current() instanceof ShapeDrawingGd
88                        ) {
89                            // Write relationship for image drawing
90                            $this->writeRelationship(
91                                $objWriter,
92                                $relId,
93                                'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/image',
94                                '../media/' . str_replace(' ', '_', $iterator2->current()->getIndexedFilename())
95                            );
96                            $iterator2->current()->relationId = 'rId' . $relId;
97                            ++$relId;
98                        } elseif ($iterator2->current() instanceof ShapeChart) {
99                            // Write relationship for chart drawing
100                            $this->writeRelationship(
101                                $objWriter,
102                                $relId,
103                                'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/chart',
104                                '../charts/' . $iterator2->current()->getIndexedFilename()
105                            );
106                            $iterator2->current()->relationId = 'rId' . $relId;
107                            ++$relId;
108                        }
109                        $iterator2->next();
110                    }
111                }
112                $iterator->next();
113            }
114        }
115
116        return $relId;
117    }

119    /**
120     * @param array<int, AbstractShape>|ArrayObject<int, AbstractShape> $shapes
121     * @param int $shapeId
122     *
123     * @throws \Exception
124     */
125    protected function writeShapeCollection(XMLWriter $objWriter, $shapes = [], &$shapeId = 0): void
126    {
127        if (0 == count($shapes)) {
128            return;
129        }
130        foreach ($shapes as $shape) {
131            // Increment $shapeId
132            ++$shapeId;
133            // Check type
134            if ($shape instanceof RichText) {
135                $this->writeShapeText($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
136            } elseif ($shape instanceof ShapeTable) {
137                $this->writeShapeTable($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
138            } elseif ($shape instanceof Line) {
139                $this->writeShapeLine($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
140            } elseif ($shape instanceof ShapeChart) {
141                $this->writeShapeChart($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
142            } elseif ($shape instanceof AbstractGraphic) {
143                $this->writeShapePic($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
144            } elseif ($shape instanceof Group) {
145                $this->writeShapeGroup($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
146            } elseif ($shape instanceof Comment) {
147            } else {
148                throw new \Exception(sprintf('Unknown Shape type: %s', get_class($shape)));
149            }
150        }
151    }

161    {
162        // p:sp
163        $objWriter->startElement('p:sp');
164        // p:sp\p:nvSpPr
165        $objWriter->startElement('p:nvSpPr');
166        // p:sp\p:nvSpPr\p:cNvPr
167        $objWriter->startElement('p:cNvPr');
168        $objWriter->writeAttribute('id', $shapeId);
169        if ($shape->isPlaceholder()) {
170            $objWriter->writeAttribute('name', 'Placeholder for ' . $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType());
171        } else {
172            $objWriter->writeAttribute('name', '');
173        }
174        // Hyperlink
175        if ($shape->hasHyperlink()) {
176            $this->writeHyperlink($objWriter, $shape);
177        }
178        // > p:sp\p:nvSpPr
179        $objWriter->endElement();
180        // p:sp\p:cNvSpPr
181        $objWriter->startElement('p:cNvSpPr');
182        $objWriter->writeAttribute('txBox', '1');
183        $objWriter->endElement();
184        // p:sp\p:cNvSpPr\p:nvPr
185        if ($shape->isPlaceholder()) {
186            $objWriter->startElement('p:nvPr');
187            $objWriter->startElement('p:ph');
188            $objWriter->writeAttribute('type', $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType());
189            if (!is_null($shape->getPlaceholder()->getIdx())) {
190                $objWriter->writeAttribute('idx', $shape->getPlaceholder()->getIdx());
191            }
192            $objWriter->endElement();
193            $objWriter->endElement();
194        } else {
195            $objWriter->writeElement('p:nvPr', null);
196        }
197        // > p:sp\p:cNvSpPr
198        $objWriter->endElement();
199        // p:sp\p:spPr
200        $objWriter->startElement('p:spPr');
201
202        if (!$shape->isPlaceholder()) {
203            // p:sp\p:spPr\a:xfrm
204            $objWriter->startElement('a:xfrm');
205            $objWriter->writeAttributeIf(0 != $shape->getRotation(), 'rot', CommonDrawing::degreesToAngle($shape->getRotation()));
206            // p:sp\p:spPr\a:xfrm\a:off
207            $objWriter->startElement('a:off');
208            $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetX()));
209            $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetY()));
210            $objWriter->endElement();
211            // p:sp\p:spPr\a:xfrm\a:ext
212            $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
213            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getWidth()));
214            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getHeight()));
215            $objWriter->endElement();
216            // > p:sp\p:spPr\a:xfrm
217            $objWriter->endElement();
218            // p:sp\p:spPr\a:prstGeom
219            $objWriter->startElement('a:prstGeom');
220            $objWriter->writeAttribute('prst', 'rect');
221
222            // p:sp\p:spPr\a:prstGeom\a:avLst
223            $objWriter->writeElement('a:avLst');
224
225            $objWriter->endElement();
226        }
227        $this->writeFill($objWriter, $shape->getFill());
228        $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $shape->getBorder(), '');
229        $this->writeShadow($objWriter, $shape->getShadow());
230
231        // > p:sp\p:spPr
232        $objWriter->endElement();
233        // p:txBody
234        $objWriter->startElement('p:txBody');
235        // a:bodyPr
236        //@link :http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/documentformat.openxml.drawing.bodyproperties%28v=office.14%29.aspx
237        $objWriter->startElement('a:bodyPr');
238        if (!$shape->isPlaceholder()) {
239            $verticalAlign = $shape->getActiveParagraph()->getAlignment()->getVertical();
240            if (Alignment::VERTICAL_BASE != $verticalAlign && Alignment::VERTICAL_AUTO != $verticalAlign) {
241                $objWriter->writeAttribute('anchor', $verticalAlign);
242            }
243            if (RichText::WRAP_SQUARE != $shape->getWrap()) {
244                $objWriter->writeAttribute('wrap', $shape->getWrap());
245            }
246            $objWriter->writeAttribute('rtlCol', '0');
247            if (RichText::OVERFLOW_OVERFLOW != $shape->getHorizontalOverflow()) {
248                $objWriter->writeAttribute('horzOverflow', $shape->getHorizontalOverflow());
249            }
250            if (RichText::OVERFLOW_OVERFLOW != $shape->getVerticalOverflow()) {
251                $objWriter->writeAttribute('vertOverflow', $shape->getVerticalOverflow());
252            }
253            if ($shape->isUpright()) {
254                $objWriter->writeAttribute('upright', '1');
255            }
256            if ($shape->isVertical()) {
257                $objWriter->writeAttribute('vert', 'vert');
258            }
259            $objWriter->writeAttribute('bIns', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getInsetBottom()));
260            $objWriter->writeAttribute('lIns', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getInsetLeft()));
261            $objWriter->writeAttribute('rIns', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getInsetRight()));
262            $objWriter->writeAttribute('tIns', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getInsetTop()));
263            if (1 != $shape->getColumns()) {
264                $objWriter->writeAttribute('numCol', $shape->getColumns());
265            }
266            // a:spAutoFit
267            $objWriter->startElement('a:' . $shape->getAutoFit());
268            if (RichText::AUTOFIT_NORMAL == $shape->getAutoFit()) {
269                if (!is_null($shape->getFontScale())) {
270                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('fontScale', $shape->getFontScale() * 1000);
271                }
272                if (!is_null($shape->getLineSpaceReduction())) {
273                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('lnSpcReduction', $shape->getLineSpaceReduction() * 1000);
274                }
275            }
276            $objWriter->endElement();
277        }
278        $objWriter->endElement();
279        // a:lstStyle
280        $objWriter->writeElement('a:lstStyle', null);
281        if ($shape->isPlaceholder() &&
282            (Placeholder::PH_TYPE_SLIDENUM == $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType() ||
283                Placeholder::PH_TYPE_DATETIME == $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType())
284        ) {
285            $objWriter->startElement('a:p');

288            $objWriter->writeAttribute('type', (
289                Placeholder::PH_TYPE_SLIDENUM == $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType() ? 'slidenum' : 'datetime'
290            ));
291            $objWriter->writeElement('a:t', (
292                Placeholder::PH_TYPE_SLIDENUM == $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType() ? '<nr.>' : '03-04-05'
293            ));
294            $objWriter->endElement();
295            $objWriter->endElement();
296        } else {
297            // Write paragraphs
298            $this->writeParagraphs($objWriter, $shape->getParagraphs());
299        }
300        $objWriter->endElement();
301        $objWriter->endElement();
302    }

346        $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetY()));
347        $objWriter->endElement();
348        // p:graphicFrame/p:xfrm/a:ext

352        $objWriter->endElement();
353        // p:graphicFrame/p:xfrm/
354        $objWriter->endElement();
355        // p:graphicFrame/a:graphic
356        $objWriter->startElement('a:graphic');
357        // p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData
358        $objWriter->startElement('a:graphicData');
359        $objWriter->writeAttribute('uri', 'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/drawingml/2006/table');
360        // p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData/a:tbl
361        $objWriter->startElement('a:tbl');
362        // p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData/a:tbl/a:tblPr
363        $objWriter->startElement('a:tblPr');
364        $objWriter->writeAttribute('firstRow', '1');

367        // p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData/a:tbl/a:tblGrid
368        $objWriter->startElement('a:tblGrid');
369        // Write cell widths
370        $countCells = count($shape->getRow(0)->getCells());
371        for ($cell = 0; $cell < $countCells; ++$cell) {
372            //  p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData/a:tbl/a:tblGrid/a:gridCol
373            $objWriter->startElement('a:gridCol');
374            // Calculate column width
375            $width = $shape->getRow(0)->getCell($cell)->getWidth();
376            if (0 == $width) {
377                $colCount = count($shape->getRow(0)->getCells());
378                $totalWidth = $shape->getWidth();
379                $width = $totalWidth / $colCount;
380            }
381            $objWriter->writeAttribute('w', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($width));
382            $objWriter->endElement();
383        }
384        // p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData/a:tbl/a:tblGrid/
385        $objWriter->endElement();

390        $defaultBorder = new Border();
391        // Write rows
392        $countRows = count($shape->getRows());
393        for ($row = 0; $row < $countRows; ++$row) {
394            // p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData/a:tbl/a:tr
395            $objWriter->startElement('a:tr');
396            $objWriter->writeAttribute('h', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getRow($row)->getHeight()));
397            // Write cells
398            $countCells = count($shape->getRow($row)->getCells());
399            for ($cell = 0; $cell < $countCells; ++$cell) {
400                // Current cell
401                $currentCell = $shape->getRow($row)->getCell($cell);
402                // Next cell right
403                $nextCellRight = $shape->getRow($row)->getCell($cell + 1, true);
404                // Next cell below
405                $nextRowBelow = $shape->getRow($row + 1, true);
406                $nextCellBelow = null;
407                if (null != $nextRowBelow) {
408                    $nextCellBelow = $nextRowBelow->getCell($cell, true);
409                }
410                // a:tc
411                $objWriter->startElement('a:tc');
412                // Colspan
413                if ($currentCell->getColSpan() > 1) {
414                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('gridSpan', $currentCell->getColSpan());
415                    $colSpan[$row] = $currentCell->getColSpan() - 1;
416                } elseif (isset($colSpan[$row]) && $colSpan[$row] > 0) {
417                    --$colSpan[$row];
418                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('hMerge', '1');
419                }
420                // Rowspan
421                if ($currentCell->getRowSpan() > 1) {
422                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('rowSpan', $currentCell->getRowSpan());
423                    $rowSpan[$cell] = $currentCell->getRowSpan() - 1;
424                } elseif (isset($rowSpan[$cell]) && $rowSpan[$cell] > 0) {
425                    --$rowSpan[$cell];
426                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('vMerge', '1');
427                }
428                // a:txBody
429                $objWriter->startElement('a:txBody');
430                // a:txBody/a:bodyPr
431                $objWriter->startElement('a:bodyPr');
432                $objWriter->writeAttribute('wrap', 'square');
433                $objWriter->writeAttribute('rtlCol', '0');
434                // a:txBody/a:bodyPr/a:spAutoFit
435                $objWriter->writeElement('a:spAutoFit', null);
436                // a:txBody/a:bodyPr/
437                $objWriter->endElement();
438                // a:lstStyle
439                $objWriter->writeElement('a:lstStyle', null);
440                // Write paragraphs
441                $this->writeParagraphs($objWriter, $currentCell->getParagraphs());
442                $objWriter->endElement();
443                // a:tcPr
444                $objWriter->startElement('a:tcPr');
445                $firstParagraph = $currentCell->getParagraph(0);
446                $firstParagraphAlignment = $firstParagraph->getAlignment();
447
448                // Text Direction
449                $textDirection = $firstParagraphAlignment->getTextDirection();
450                if (Alignment::TEXT_DIRECTION_HORIZONTAL != $textDirection) {
451                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('vert', $textDirection);
452                }
453                // Alignment (horizontal)
454                $verticalAlign = $firstParagraphAlignment->getVertical();
455                if (Alignment::VERTICAL_BASE != $verticalAlign && Alignment::VERTICAL_AUTO != $verticalAlign) {
456                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('anchor', $verticalAlign);
457                }
458
459                // Margins
460                $objWriter->writeAttribute('marL', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($firstParagraphAlignment->getMarginLeft()));
461                $objWriter->writeAttribute('marR', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($firstParagraphAlignment->getMarginRight()));
462                $objWriter->writeAttribute('marT', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($firstParagraphAlignment->getMarginTop()));
463                $objWriter->writeAttribute('marB', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($firstParagraphAlignment->getMarginBottom()));
464
465                // Determine borders
466                $borderLeft = $currentCell->getBorders()->getLeft();
467                $borderRight = $currentCell->getBorders()->getRight();
468                $borderTop = $currentCell->getBorders()->getTop();
469                $borderBottom = $currentCell->getBorders()->getBottom();
470                $borderDiagonalDown = $currentCell->getBorders()->getDiagonalDown();
471                $borderDiagonalUp = $currentCell->getBorders()->getDiagonalUp();
472                // Fix PowerPoint implementation
473                if (!is_null($nextCellRight)
474                    && $nextCellRight->getBorders()->getRight()->getHashCode() != $defaultBorder->getHashCode()
475                ) {
476                    $borderRight = $nextCellRight->getBorders()->getLeft();
477                }
478                if (!is_null($nextCellBelow)
479                    && $nextCellBelow->getBorders()->getBottom()->getHashCode() != $defaultBorder->getHashCode()
480                ) {
481                    $borderBottom = $nextCellBelow->getBorders()->getTop();
482                }
483                // Write borders
484                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderLeft, 'L');
485                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderRight, 'R');
486                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderTop, 'T');
487                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderBottom, 'B');
488                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderDiagonalDown, 'TlToBr');
489                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderDiagonalUp, 'BlToTr');
490                // Fill
491                $this->writeFill($objWriter, $currentCell->getFill());
492                $objWriter->endElement();
493                $objWriter->endElement();
494            }
495            $objWriter->endElement();
496        }
497        $objWriter->endElement();
498        $objWriter->endElement();
499        $objWriter->endElement();
500        $objWriter->endElement();
501    }
502
503    /**
504     * Write paragraphs.
505     *
506     * @param XMLWriter $objWriter XML Writer
507     * @param array<Paragraph> $paragraphs
508     *
509     * @throws \Exception
510     */
511    protected function writeParagraphs(XMLWriter $objWriter, array $paragraphs, bool $bIsPlaceholder = false): void
512    {
513        // Loop trough paragraphs
514        foreach ($paragraphs as $paragraph) {
515            // a:p
516            $objWriter->startElement('a:p');
517
518            // a:pPr
519            if (!$bIsPlaceholder) {
520                $objWriter->startElement('a:pPr');
521                $objWriter->writeAttribute('algn', $paragraph->getAlignment()->getHorizontal());
522                $objWriter->writeAttribute('fontAlgn', $paragraph->getAlignment()->getVertical());
523                $objWriter->writeAttribute('marL', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($paragraph->getAlignment()->getMarginLeft()));
524                $objWriter->writeAttribute('marR', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($paragraph->getAlignment()->getMarginRight()));
525                $objWriter->writeAttribute('indent', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($paragraph->getAlignment()->getIndent()));
526                $objWriter->writeAttribute('lvl', $paragraph->getAlignment()->getLevel());
527
528                $objWriter->startElement('a:lnSpc');
529                $objWriter->startElement('a:spcPct');
530                $objWriter->writeAttribute('val', $paragraph->getLineSpacing() * 1000);
531                $objWriter->endElement();
532                $objWriter->endElement();
533
534                // Bullet type specified?
535                if (Bullet::TYPE_NONE != $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletType()) {
536                    // Color
537                    // a:buClr must be before a:buFont (else PowerPoint crashes at launch)
538                    if ($paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletColor() instanceof Color) {
539                        $objWriter->startElement('a:buClr');
540                        $this->writeColor($objWriter, $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletColor());
541                        $objWriter->endElement();
542                    }
543
544                    // a:buFont
545                    $objWriter->startElement('a:buFont');
546                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('typeface', $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletFont());
547                    $objWriter->endElement();
548
549                    if (Bullet::TYPE_BULLET == $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletType()) {
550                        // a:buChar
551                        $objWriter->startElement('a:buChar');
552                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('char', $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletChar());
553                        $objWriter->endElement();
554                    } elseif (Bullet::TYPE_NUMERIC == $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletType()) {
555                        // a:buAutoNum
556                        $objWriter->startElement('a:buAutoNum');
557                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('type', $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletNumericStyle());
558                        if (1 != $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletNumericStartAt()) {
559                            $objWriter->writeAttribute('startAt', $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletNumericStartAt());
560                        }
561                        $objWriter->endElement();
562                    }
563                }
564
565                $objWriter->endElement();
566            }
567
568            // Loop trough rich text elements
569            $elements = $paragraph->getRichTextElements();
570            foreach ($elements as $element) {
571                if ($element instanceof BreakElement) {
572                    // a:br
573                    $objWriter->writeElement('a:br', null);
574                } elseif ($element instanceof Run || $element instanceof TextElement) {
575                    // a:r
576                    $objWriter->startElement('a:r');
577
578                    // a:rPr
579                    if ($element instanceof Run && !$bIsPlaceholder) {
580                        // a:rPr
581                        $objWriter->startElement('a:rPr');
582
583                        // Lang
584                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('lang', ($element->getLanguage() ? $element->getLanguage() : 'en-US'));
585                        $objWriter->writeAttributeIf($element->getFont()->isBold(), 'b', '1');
586                        $objWriter->writeAttributeIf($element->getFont()->isItalic(), 'i', '1');
587                        $objWriter->writeAttributeIf($element->getFont()->isStrikethrough(), 'strike', 'sngStrike');
588                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('sz', ($element->getFont()->getSize() * 100));
589                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('spc', $element->getFont()->getCharacterSpacing());
590                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('u', $element->getFont()->getUnderline());
591                        $objWriter->writeAttributeIf($element->getFont()->isSuperScript(), 'baseline', '300000');
592                        $objWriter->writeAttributeIf($element->getFont()->isSubScript(), 'baseline', '-250000');
593
594                        // Color - a:solidFill
595                        $objWriter->startElement('a:solidFill');
596                        $this->writeColor($objWriter, $element->getFont()->getColor());
597                        $objWriter->endElement();
598
599                        // Font - a:latin
600                        $objWriter->startElement('a:latin');
601                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('typeface', $element->getFont()->getName());
602                        $objWriter->endElement();
603
604                        // a:hlinkClick
605                        $this->writeHyperlink($objWriter, $element);
606
607                        $objWriter->endElement();
608                    }
609
610                    // t
611                    $objWriter->startElement('a:t');
612                    $objWriter->writeCData(Text::controlCharacterPHP2OOXML($element->getText()));
613                    $objWriter->endElement();
614
615                    $objWriter->endElement();
616                }
617            }
618
619            $objWriter->endElement();
620        }
621    }
622
623    /**
624     * Write Line Shape.
625     *
626     * @param XMLWriter $objWriter XML Writer
627     *
628     * @throws \Exception
629     */
630    protected function writeShapeLine(XMLWriter $objWriter, Line $shape, int $shapeId): void
631    {
632        // p:sp
633        $objWriter->startElement('p:cxnSp');
634        // p:nvSpPr
635        $objWriter->startElement('p:nvCxnSpPr');
636        // p:cNvPr
637        $objWriter->startElement('p:cNvPr');
638        $objWriter->writeAttribute('id', $shapeId);
639        $objWriter->writeAttribute('name', '');
640        $objWriter->endElement();
641        // p:cNvCxnSpPr
642        $objWriter->writeElement('p:cNvCxnSpPr', null);
643        // p:nvPr
644        $objWriter->startElement('p:nvPr');
645        if ($shape->isPlaceholder()) {
646            $objWriter->startElement('p:ph');
647            $objWriter->writeAttribute('type', $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType());
648            $objWriter->endElement();
649        }
650        $objWriter->endElement();
651        $objWriter->endElement();
652        // p:spPr
653        $objWriter->startElement('p:spPr');
654        // a:xfrm
655        $objWriter->startElement('a:xfrm');
656        if ($shape->getWidth() >= 0 && $shape->getHeight() >= 0) {
657            // a:off
658            $objWriter->startElement('a:off');
659            $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetX()));
660            $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetY()));
661            $objWriter->endElement();
662            // a:ext
663            $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
664            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getWidth()));
665            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getHeight()));
666            $objWriter->endElement();
667        } elseif ($shape->getWidth() < 0 && $shape->getHeight() < 0) {
668            // a:off
669            $objWriter->startElement('a:off');
670            $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetX() + $shape->getWidth()));
671            $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetY() + $shape->getHeight()));
672            $objWriter->endElement();
673            // a:ext
674            $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
675            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu(-$shape->getWidth()));
676            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu(-$shape->getHeight()));
677            $objWriter->endElement();
678        } elseif ($shape->getHeight() < 0) {
679            $objWriter->writeAttribute('flipV', 1);
680            // a:off
681            $objWriter->startElement('a:off');
682            $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetX()));
683            $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetY() + $shape->getHeight()));
684            $objWriter->endElement();
685            // a:ext
686            $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
687            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getWidth()));
688            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu(-$shape->getHeight()));
689            $objWriter->endElement();
690        } elseif ($shape->getWidth() < 0) {
691            $objWriter->writeAttribute('flipV', 1);
692            // a:off
693            $objWriter->startElement('a:off');
694            $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetX() + $shape->getWidth()));
695            $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetY()));
696            $objWriter->endElement();
697            // a:ext
698            $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
699            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu(-$shape->getWidth()));
700            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getHeight()));
701            $objWriter->endElement();
702        }
703        $objWriter->endElement();
704        // a:prstGeom
705        $objWriter->startElement('a:prstGeom');
706        $objWriter->writeAttribute('prst', 'line');
707
708        // a:prstGeom/a:avLst
709        $objWriter->writeElement('a:avLst');
710
711        $objWriter->endElement();
712        $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $shape->getBorder(), '');
713        $objWriter->endElement();
714        $objWriter->endElement();
715    }

717    /**
718     * Write Shadow.
719     */
720    protected function writeShadow(XMLWriter $objWriter, Shadow $oShadow): void
721    {
722        if (!($oShadow instanceof Shadow)) {
723            return;
724        }
725
726        if (!$oShadow->isVisible()) {
727            return;
728        }
729
730        // a:effectLst
731        $objWriter->startElement('a:effectLst');
732
733        // a:outerShdw
734        $objWriter->startElement('a:outerShdw');
735        $objWriter->writeAttribute('blurRad', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($oShadow->getBlurRadius()));
736        $objWriter->writeAttribute('dist', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($oShadow->getDistance()));
737        $objWriter->writeAttribute('dir', CommonDrawing::degreesToAngle($oShadow->getDirection()));
738        $objWriter->writeAttribute('algn', $oShadow->getAlignment());
739        $objWriter->writeAttribute('rotWithShape', '0');
740
741        $this->writeColor($objWriter, $oShadow->getColor(), $oShadow->getAlpha());
742
743        $objWriter->endElement();
744
745        $objWriter->endElement();
746    }

748    /**
749     * Write hyperlink.
750     *
751     * @param XMLWriter $objWriter XML Writer
752     * @param AbstractShape|TextElement $shape
753     *
754     * @throws \Exception
755     */
756    protected function writeHyperlink(XMLWriter $objWriter, $shape): void
757    {
758        if (!$shape->hasHyperlink()) {
759            return;
760        }
761        // a:hlinkClick
762        $objWriter->startElement('a:hlinkClick');
763        $objWriter->writeAttribute('r:id', $shape->getHyperlink()->relationId);
764        $objWriter->writeAttribute('tooltip', $shape->getHyperlink()->getTooltip());
765        if ($shape->getHyperlink()->isInternal()) {
766            $objWriter->writeAttribute('action', $shape->getHyperlink()->getUrl());
767        }
768        $objWriter->endElement();
769    }

771    /**
772     * Write Note Slide.
773     *
774     * @throws \Exception
775     */
776    protected function writeNote(Note $pNote): string
777    {
778        // Create XML writer
779        $objWriter = new XMLWriter(XMLWriter::STORAGE_MEMORY);
780
781        // XML header
782        $objWriter->startDocument('1.0', 'UTF-8', 'yes');
783
784        // p:notes
785        $objWriter->startElement('p:notes');
786        $objWriter->writeAttribute('xmlns:a', 'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/drawingml/2006/main');
787        $objWriter->writeAttribute('xmlns:p', 'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/presentationml/2006/main');
788        $objWriter->writeAttribute('xmlns:r', 'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships');
789
790        // p:notes/p:cSld
791        $objWriter->startElement('p:cSld');
792
793        // p:notes/p:cSld/p:spTree
794        $objWriter->startElement('p:spTree');
795
796        // p:notes/p:cSld/p:spTree/p:nvGrpSpPr
797        $objWriter->startElement('p:nvGrpSpPr');
798
799        // p:notes/p:cSld/p:spTree/p:nvGrpSpPr/p:cNvPr
800        $objWriter->startElement('p:cNvPr');
801        $objWriter->writeAttribute('id', '1');
802        $objWriter->writeAttribute('name', '');
803        $objWriter->endElement();
804
805        // p:notes/p:cSld/p:spTree/p:nvGrpSpPr/p:cNvGrpSpPr
806        $objWriter->writeElement('p:cNvGrpSpPr', null);
807
808        // p:notes/p:cSld/p:spTree/p:nvGrpSpPr/p:nvPr
809        $objWriter->writeElement('p:nvPr', null);
810
811        // p:notes/p:cSld/p:spTree/p:nvGrpSpPr
812        $objWriter->endElement();
813
814        // p:notes/p:cSld/p:spTree/p:grpSpPr
815        $objWriter->startElement('p:grpSpPr');
816
817        // p:notes/p:cSld/p:spTree/p:grpSpPr/a:xfrm
818        $objWriter->startElement('a:xfrm');
819
820        // p:notes/p:cSld/p:spTree/p:grpSpPr/a:xfrm/a:off
821        $objWriter->startElement('a:off');
822        $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($pNote->getOffsetX()));
823        $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($pNote->getOffsetY()));
824        $objWriter->endElement(); // a:off
825
826        // p:notes/p:cSld/p:spTree/p:grpSpPr/a:xfrm/a:ext
827        $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
828        $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($pNote->getExtentX()));
829        $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($pNote->getExtentY()));
830        $objWriter->endElement(); // a:ext
831
832        // p:notes/p:cSld/p:spTree/p:grpSpPr/a:xfrm/a:chOff
833        $objWriter->startElement('a:chOff');
834        $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($pNote->getOffsetX()));
835        $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($pNote->getOffsetY()));
836        $objWriter->endElement(); // a:chOff
837
838        // p:notes/p:cSld/p:spTree/p:grpSpPr/a:xfrm/a:chExt
839        $objWriter->startElement('a:chExt');
840        $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($pNote->getExtentX()));
841        $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($pNote->getExtentY()));
